<b>Microsoft and Sega Confirmation</b> - True Red 20:08 pm 03-29-01
</table></div>

<div class=itemtext>
The X-box is going to supported by Sega: <p> <i>The daily grind was rudely interrupted earlier this week by a rumor that sent shock waves through the Xbox community, and now Microsoft and Sega have confirmed that the two are conspiring to bring the upcoming console a host of quality titles in the next 12 months.  Sega, a new player on the 3rd party publishing scene, has confirmed that they will be bringing no fewer than 11 titles to the Xbox.</i> <p> You can read the rest of the article <a href="http://xbox.ign.com/news/32897.html" target="_blank">here</a>.<br>
