<b>Lumina into NiGHTS</b> - Sierra Ranay 13:33 pm 03-13-01
</table></div>

<div class=itemtext>
In Sonic Shuffle, you can change Lumina into NiGHTS. I found this out from  the Technomania section of "Disney Adventures" (April 2001 issue):<P> <I>"Fool your friends by changing the character of Lumina the fairy into the Nights charatcer (star of the classic <B>Nights</B> game). To do it, go to your Dreamcast's Settings menu and change the date to Christmas Eve, 12/24/00. Then head back to the game and you'll have a whole new character. That's a Christmas present you can use year-round!"<I><P><B>Source:</B><I>Disney Adventures Magazine</I><br>
