<b>SAGE is open!</b> - Mike 3:49 am 03-10-01
</table></div>

<div class=itemtext>
The Sonic amature games expo is once again open for a 5 day period!  For those who arn't in the know, SAGE is a yearly event where the top Sonic fan game creators go to show off their upcoming releases to the outside world. This year, there are about 20 booths showing off brand new demos of games such as SRB2, Thirdscape, TFH, Metal Sonics quest 2, Sonic Forever and many more.  Fancy checking it out? www.sagexpo.org<br>
</div><div class=titlebar><table class=glow>
