<b>Sonic in _NINTENDO_ Power</b> - TLSPRWR(First time poster) 16:01 pm 03-08-01
</table></div>

<div class=itemtext>
Reading through the latest <a href="http://www.nintendopower.com/">Nintendo Power</a> I stubled across an article about Sega developing for GBA (GameBoy Advance) and GCN (GameCube). Finding this rather surprising, I read through the whole article which was mostly about the GBA games Sega is developing. The titles anounced were ChuChu Rocket GBA ( or ChuChu Rocket Advance), Puyo Puyo, and Sonic Advance. No GCN titles were anounced.<br>
